Ruby Version - 1.9.3-p448
Rails Version - 3.2.12

Database Server - MySQL 5.5

installation on ubuntu => sudo apt-get install mysql-server mysql-client

Gems Required - 

'mysql2'
'activerecord-mysql-adapter'
'will_paginate'
'execjs'
'therubyracer'

getting gems => gem install 'gem_name'

MySQL drivers

'libmysql-ruby'
'libmysqlclient-dev'

installing on ubuntu => sudo apt-get install libmysql-ruby libmysqlclient-dev
